{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1643,"text":"All right, so let's take"},{"time":2782,"text":"four subjects that obviously go together:"},{"time":5122,"text":"big data, tattoos, immortality and the Greeks."},{"time":9851,"text":"Right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":10681,"text":"Now, the issue about tattoos is that,"},{"time":14100,"text":"without a word, tattoos really do shout."},{"time":18305,"text":"[Beautiful]"},{"time":22365,"text":"[Intriguing]"},{"time":24263,"text":"So you don't have to say a lot."},{"time":27578,"text":"[Allegiance]"},{"time":31246,"text":"[Very intimate]"},{"time":35648,"text":"[Serious mistakes]"},{"time":38273,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":42437,"text":"And tattoos tell you a lot of stories."},{"time":46218,"text":"If I can ask an indiscreet question,"},{"time":47963,"text":"how many of you have tattoos?"},{"time":51439,"text":"A few, but not most."},{"time":52946,"text":"What happens if Facebook, Google, Twitter, LinkedIn,"},{"time":55733,"text":"cell phones, GPS, Foursquare, Yelp, Travel Advisor,"},{"time":58631,"text":"all these things you deal with every day"},{"time":61391,"text":"turn out to be electronic tattoos?"},{"time":63751,"text":"And what if they provide as much information"},{"time":65373,"text":"about who and what you are as any tattoo ever would?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":70350,"text":"What's ended up happening over the past few decades"},{"time":72536,"text":"is the kind of coverage that you had as a head of state"},{"time":75642,"text":"or as a great celebrity"},{"time":78321,"text":"is now being applied to you every day by all these people"},{"time":81042,"text":"who are Tweeting, blogging, following you,"},{"time":84029,"text":"watching your credit scores and what you do to yourself."},{"time":88349,"text":"And electronic tattoos also shout."},{"time":92763,"text":"And as you're thinking of the consequences of that,"},{"time":95107,"text":"it's getting really hard to hide from this stuff, among other things,"},{"time":98043,"text":"because it's not just the electronic tattoos,"},{"time":100822,"text":"it's facial recognition that's getting really good."},{"time":104894,"text":"So you can take a picture with an iPhone and get all the names,"},{"time":108692,"text":"although, again, sometimes it does make mistakes. (Laughter)"},{"time":112749,"text":"But that means you can take a typical bar scene like this,"},{"time":115758,"text":"take a picture, say, of this guy right here,"},{"time":119766,"text":"get the name, and download all the records"},{"time":123430,"text":"before you utter a word or speak to somebody,"},{"time":127049,"text":"because everybody turns out to be"},{"time":128425,"text":"absolutely plastered by electronic tattoos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132026,"text":"And so there's companies like face.com that now have"},{"time":134518,"text":"about 18 billion faces online."},{"time":138302,"text":"Here's what happened to this company."},{"time":139891,"text":"[Company sold to Facebook, June 18, 2012...]"},{"time":142554,"text":"There are other companies that will place a camera"},{"time":145207,"text":"like this — this has nothing to do with Facebook —"},{"time":147630,"text":"they take your picture, they tie it to the social media,"},{"time":149942,"text":"they figure out you really like to wear black dresses,"},{"time":152069,"text":"so maybe the person in the store comes up and says,"},{"time":154505,"text":"\"Hey, we've got five black dresses"},{"time":156805,"text":"that would just look great on you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":160038,"text":"So what if Andy was wrong?"},{"time":162158,"text":"Here's Andy's theory."},{"time":163428,"text":"[In the future, everybody will be world famous for 15 minutes.]"},{"time":165272,"text":"What if we flip this?"},{"time":166378,"text":"What if you're only going to be anonymous for 15 minutes? (Laughter)"},{"time":171059,"text":"Well, then, because of electronic tattoos,"},{"time":174075,"text":"maybe all of you and all of us are very close to immortality,"},{"time":178736,"text":"because these tattoos will live"},{"time":180314,"text":"far longer than our bodies will."},{"time":183091,"text":"And if that's true, then what we want to do"},{"time":184982,"text":"is we want to go through four lessons from the Greeks"},{"time":188391,"text":"and one lesson from a Latin American."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191700,"text":"Why the Greeks?"},{"time":193523,"text":"Well, the Greeks thought about what happens"},{"time":195380,"text":"when gods and humans and immortality mix for a long time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200338,"text":"So lesson number one: Sisyphus."},{"time":203018,"text":"Remember? He did a horrible thing, condemned for all time"},{"time":206044,"text":"to roll this rock up, it would roll back down,"},{"time":208427,"text":"roll back up, roll back down."},{"time":210400,"text":"It's a little like your reputation."},{"time":212803,"text":"Once you get that electronic tattoo,"},{"time":214238,"text":"you're going to be rolling up and down for a long time,"},{"time":217166,"text":"so as you go through this stuff,"},{"time":219474,"text":"just be careful what you post."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222559,"text":"Myth number two: Orpheus, wonderful guy,"},{"time":225938,"text":"charming to be around, great partier, great singer,"},{"time":229666,"text":"loses his beloved, charms his way into the underworld,"},{"time":232883,"text":"only person to charm his way into the underworld,"},{"time":235490,"text":"charms the gods of the underworld,"},{"time":237835,"text":"they release his beauty on the condition"},{"time":240730,"text":"he never look at her until they're out."},{"time":243842,"text":"So he's walking out and walking out and walking out"},{"time":245681,"text":"and he just can't resist. He looks at her, loses her forever."},{"time":249939,"text":"With all this data out here, it might be a good idea"},{"time":252773,"text":"not to look too far into the past of those you love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258521,"text":"Lesson number three: Atalanta."},{"time":261362,"text":"Greatest runner. She would challenge anybody."},{"time":265811,"text":"If you won, she would marry you."},{"time":268221,"text":"If you lost, you died."},{"time":271146,"text":"How did Hippomenes beat her?"},{"time":273490,"text":"Well, he had all these wonderful little golden apples,"},{"time":275416,"text":"and she'd run ahead, and he'd roll a little golden apple."},{"time":278034,"text":"She'd run ahead, and he'd roll a little golden apple."},{"time":280038,"text":"She kept getting distracted. He eventually won the race."},{"time":284284,"text":"Just remember the purpose as all these little golden apples"},{"time":287514,"text":"come and reach you and you want to post about them"},{"time":290086,"text":"or tweet about them or send a late-night message."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293922,"text":"And then, of course, there's Narcissus."},{"time":297170,"text":"Nobody here would ever be accused or be familiar with Narcissus."},{"time":300717,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":303013,"text":"But as you're thinking about Narcissus,"},{"time":305581,"text":"just don't fall in love with your own reflection."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309661,"text":"Last lesson, from a Latin American:"},{"time":311452,"text":"This is the great poet Jorge Luis Borges."},{"time":314213,"text":"When he was threatened by the thugs"},{"time":315402,"text":"of the Argentine military junta,"},{"time":318035,"text":"he came back and said, \"Oh, come on,"},{"time":320288,"text":"how else can you threaten, other than with death?\""},{"time":323733,"text":"The interesting thing, the original thing,"},{"time":326853,"text":"would be to threaten somebody with immortality."},{"time":330045,"text":"And that, of course, is what we are all"},{"time":331505,"text":"now threatened with today because of electronic tattoos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335681,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336766,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}